# Build context is `containers/ci/` (see build-ci-image.yml `context:`).
#
# Only `sanity.sh` is COPY'd into the image; the Dockerfile itself is
# read by buildx via `file:` and doesn't need to ship in the context.
# Excluding everything else keeps the context tiny so cache hits are
# stable across unrelated edits in the repo.

*
!sanity.sh
